p10
aVof African-Americans,
p11
aVand it was also really hard to hear all the stories of the horrors
p12
aVand the humility, and all the humiliations.
p13
aVIt was especially hard to hear about the beatings and the burnings
p14
aVand the lynchings of black men.
p15
aVAnd I said, "You know, this is a little deep.
