aVI need a break. I'm going to turn on the radio."
p17
aVI turned it on, and there it was:
p18
aVFerguson, Missouri,
p19
aVMichael Brown,
p20
aV18-year-old black man,
p21
aVunarmed, shot by a white police officer, laid on the ground dead,
p22
aVblood running for four hours
p23
aVwhile his grandmother and little children and his neighbors watched in horror,
p24
aVand I thought,
p25
aVhere it is again.
