aa(lp34
VThis violence, this brutality,
p35
aVis really something that's part of our national psyche.
p36
aVIt's part of our collective history.
p37
aVWhat are we going to do about it?
p38
aVYou know that part of us that still crosses the street,
p39
aVlocks the doors,
p40
aVclutches the purses,
p41
aVwhen we see young black men?
p42
aVThat part.
