aa(lp53
VSo I have a call to action for you.
p54
aVThere are three things that I want to offer us today to think about
p55
aVas ways to stop Ferguson from happening again;
p56
aVthree things that I think will help us
p57
aVreform our images of young black men;
p58
aVthree things that I'm hoping will not only protect them
p59
aVbut will open the world so that they can thrive.
p60
aVCan you imagine that?
p61
aVCan you imagine our country embracing young black men,
p62
aVseeing them as part of our future, giving them that kind of openness,
p63
aVthat kind of grace we give to people we love?
p64
aVHow much better would our lives be? How much better would our country be?
