VSo here's the thing.
p158
aVThe other possibility in science,
p159
aVand it's only temporarily changing our automatic assumptions,
p160
aVbut one thing we know
p161
aVis that if you take a white person who is odious that you know,
p162
aVand stick it up next to a person of color,
p163
aVa black person, who is fabulous,
p164
aVthen that sometimes actually causes us to disassociate too.
